sequenceDiagram
autonumber

actor User
participant ChatPage as WorkoutChatbotPage
participant WorkflowSvc as WorkoutWorkflowService
participant EstimatorPrep as WorkoutWorkflowEstimatorPreparationService
participant SummaryProjection as WorkoutWorkflowSummaryProjectionService
participant WorkoutChatSvc as WorkoutChatService
participant ChatFn as workoutChatCallable
participant OpenAI
participant LogSvc as WorkoutLogService
participant CompleteFn as completeWorkoutEvent
participant FS as Firestore
participant PostWrite as onWorkoutEventCreated
participant GroupSyncFn as onGroupDocumentWrittenSyncChat
participant EnsureGroupFn as ensureGroupChatForGroup
participant RTDB as Realtime Database
participant HistoryPage as WorkoutHistoryPage
participant SummarySvc as WorkoutSummaryService
participant SummaryPage as WorkoutSummaryPage
participant GroupSvc as GroupService
participant ChatsSvc as ChatsService
participant LeaderboardPage as LeaderboardPage
participant ClientChatsPage as ClientChatsPage
participant ChatDetail as ChatDetailPage

rect rgb(245, 248, 255)
  Note over User,PostWrite: Workout capture + persistence pipeline
  User->>ChatPage: Enter workout details
  ChatPage->>WorkflowSvc: processWorkoutMessage(message, messages, screenState)
  WorkflowSvc->>EstimatorPrep: prepareEstimatorsForSession(session)
  EstimatorPrep-->>WorkflowSvc: estimatorIds
  WorkflowSvc->>WorkoutChatSvc: sendMessage(message, session, history, estimatorIds)
  WorkoutChatSvc->>ChatFn: httpsCallable(payload)
  ChatFn->>OpenAI: parse/update structured workout data
  OpenAI-->>ChatFn: assistantMessage + summary
  ChatFn-->>WorkoutChatSvc: ChatResponse
  WorkflowSvc->>SummaryProjection: projectWorkflowState(updatedSession)
  WorkflowSvc-->>ChatPage: session + live summary rows

  User->>ChatPage: Submit workout
  ChatPage->>WorkflowSvc: submitWorkout(session, requestTrainerNotes)
  WorkflowSvc->>LogSvc: saveCompletedWorkout(session)
  LogSvc->>CompleteFn: completeWorkoutEvent(normalized WorkoutEvent)
  CompleteFn->>FS: Write users/{uid}/workoutEvents/{eventId}
  CompleteFn-->>LogSvc: { eventId, status: persisted }

  FS-->>PostWrite: Trigger on users/{uid}/workoutEvents/{eventId}
  PostWrite->>FS: Update user stats + score derivations + group war scoring
  PostWrite->>FS: Read same-day workoutEvents
  PostWrite->>FS: Upsert users/{uid}/workoutSummaries/{YYYY-MM-DD}

  alt user has trainerId
    PostWrite->>FS: Resolve trainer + user display identity
    PostWrite->>RTDB: Find or create direct chat with trainer
    alt first summary message for day
      PostWrite->>RTDB: Create chats/{chatId}/messages/workout_summary_{YYYY-MM-DD}
      PostWrite->>RTDB: Set lastMessage + lastMessageTime
      PostWrite->>RTDB: Upsert chatSummaries/{chatId} + increment trainer unreadCountByUser
    else same-day summary already exists
      PostWrite->>RTDB: Update existing workout_summary_{YYYY-MM-DD} text
      PostWrite->>RTDB: Update lastMessage
      PostWrite->>RTDB: Upsert chatSummaries/{chatId} without unread increment
    end
  end

  LogSvc->>FS: Poll derivations/workout_summary + derivations/score_aggregation
  LogSvc-->>WorkflowSvc: savedSession + scoreUpdate
  WorkflowSvc->>SummaryProjection: projectWorkflowState(savedSession)
  WorkflowSvc-->>ChatPage: saved state
end

rect rgb(246, 255, 248)
  Note over FS,RTDB: Automatic group-chat sync with membership-aware pointer writes
  FS-->>GroupSyncFn: Trigger on groupID/{groupId} write
  alt group exists AND !isPTGroup AND has members
    GroupSyncFn->>GroupSyncFn: Compare before vs after membership/name/image/PT fields
    GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Find group chat by groupId
    alt group chat exists
      GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Sync participants/displayName/groupImage/isGroupChat
      GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Upsert chatSummaries/{chatId} + unread maps
      alt membership changed
        GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Add missing userChats pointers
        GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Remove userChats pointers for removed users
      else membership unchanged
        GroupSyncFn-->>RTDB: Skip userChats pointer sync
      end
    else group chat missing
      GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Create chats/{chatId} type=group
      GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Create chatSummaries/{chatId}
      GroupSyncFn->>RTDB: Set userChats/{uid}/{chatId}=true for each member
    end
  else PT/deleted/invalid group
    GroupSyncFn-->>FS: No-op
  end
end

User->>HistoryPage: Open workout history
HistoryPage->>SummarySvc: listRecentWorkoutSummaries(uid)
SummarySvc->>FS: Read users/{uid}/workoutSummaries order by date desc
SummarySvc-->>HistoryPage: grouped daily history cards

User->>SummaryPage: Open a specific day
SummaryPage->>SummarySvc: getWorkoutSummary(uid, date)
SummarySvc->>FS: Read users/{uid}/workoutSummaries/{date}
SummarySvc-->>SummaryPage: daily summary for display

rect rgb(255, 249, 245)
  Note over User,RTDB: Open a group's chat from leaderboard (on-demand ensure)
  User->>LeaderboardPage: Tap "Go to group chat"
  LeaderboardPage->>ChatsSvc: ensureGroupChatForGroup(groupId)
  ChatsSvc->>EnsureGroupFn: httpsCallable(groupId)
  EnsureGroupFn->>FS: Read groupID/{groupId} + validate auth membership
  alt caller is member and group is not PT
    EnsureGroupFn->>RTDB: Upsert group chat metadata + participants
    EnsureGroupFn->>RTDB: Upsert chatSummaries/{chatId}
    EnsureGroupFn->>RTDB: Ensure userChats/{callerUid}/{chatId}=true
    EnsureGroupFn-->>ChatsSvc: {chatId, created}
    ChatsSvc-->>LeaderboardPage: chatId
    LeaderboardPage->>ChatDetail: Navigate /chat/{chatId}
  else permission denied / PT / not found
    EnsureGroupFn-->>LeaderboardPage: HttpsError
    LeaderboardPage-->>User: Show toast error
  end
end

rect rgb(245, 255, 255)
  Note over User,RTDB: Share workout summary to selected non-PT groups
  User->>SummaryPage: Tap "Share to Group"
  SummaryPage->>GroupSvc: getUserGroups(currentUid)
  GroupSvc->>FS: Read users/{uid}.groupID + groupID docs
  GroupSvc-->>SummaryPage: Group[]
  SummaryPage-->>User: Show modal (non-PT groups, multi-select, Select All)
  User->>SummaryPage: Confirm selected groups
  loop each selected groupId
    SummaryPage->>ChatsSvc: ensureGroupChatForGroup(groupId)
    ChatsSvc->>EnsureGroupFn: httpsCallable(groupId)
    EnsureGroupFn->>RTDB: Upsert/return group chat
    EnsureGroupFn-->>ChatsSvc: chatId
    SummaryPage->>ChatsSvc: sendWorkoutSummaryMessage(chatId, senderId, summaryText)
    ChatsSvc->>RTDB: Push chats/{chatId}/messages/{autoId} type=workout_summary
    ChatsSvc->>RTDB: Set lastMessage="Workout summary shared"
    ChatsSvc->>RTDB: Update chatSummaries/{chatId} lastMessage + unreadCountByUser
  end
  SummaryPage-->>User: Success or partial-failure toast
end

rect rgb(245, 245, 255)
  Note over User,RTDB: Chat inbox list uses summary-only subscriptions
  User->>ClientChatsPage: Open /tabs/chats/client-chats
  ClientChatsPage->>ChatsSvc: initializeUserChats(uid, accountType)
  ChatsSvc->>RTDB: Subscribe userChats/{uid}
  loop each chatId
    ChatsSvc->>RTDB: Subscribe chatSummaries/{chatId}
    alt summary missing
      ChatsSvc->>RTDB: One-time read chats/{chatId}
      ChatsSvc->>RTDB: Bootstrap chatSummaries/{chatId}
    end
  end
  ChatsSvc-->>ClientChatsPage: Emit sorted chat list
  ClientChatsPage-->>User: Render inbox without message-tree listeners
end

rect rgb(244, 252, 255)
  Note over User,RTDB: Full message stream subscription lives only in chat detail
  User->>ChatDetail: Open chat detail
  ChatDetail->>RTDB: Subscribe chats/{chatId}/messages
  RTDB-->>ChatDetail: text + workout_summary + invite/request messages
  ChatDetail->>RTDB: Mark current user read in chatSummaries/{chatId}
  ChatDetail->>FS: Read groupID/{groupId} when group chat
  ChatDetail-->>User: Render summary cards + optional members menu
end

Note over PostWrite,SummarySvc: Daily WorkoutSummary in Firestore remains the source of truth for history/persisted summary views.
Note over PostWrite,RTDB: Trainer direct chat uses deterministic workout_summary_{YYYY-MM-DD} ids and summary upserts.
Note over ChatsSvc,RTDB: Inbox unread state comes from chatSummaries unreadCountByUser/lastReadAtByUser, not message scans.
